      "content": "therapist? i dont think talking is going to change the fact that i'm just slowing them down. her life is so busy and i'm just... stuck here, needing help with every little thing. it feels like if i wasn't around, she could finally breathe and just live her own life without worrying about me constantly. it almost feels like the most selfless thing i could do is just step out of the way.",
